name: Taysa Jorge: Climbing Trees That Reach The Moon

metadata.name: Taysa Jorge: Climbing Trees That Reach The Moon
metadata.description: Climbing Trees That Reach The Moon talks about chasing your dreams and it is inspired by how I have felt in my NFT journey, same as I have felt many other times in my life. To me this piece doesn't mean sacrifice but hope and trust, and journeys that sometimes are not easy but worth it.
